ipe Mu\u00f1oz|Felipe ''Tibio'' Mu\u00f1oz]], swimming\n* [[Rommel Pacheco]], diving\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Pedraza (racewalker)|Jos\u00e9 ''Sargento'' Pedraza]], racewalker\n* [[Guillermo P\u00e9rez (taekwondo)|Guillermo P\u00e9rez]] Sandoval, taekwondo\n* [[Fernando Platas]], diving\n* [[Maria Teresa Ram\u00edrez]], swimming\n* [[Romary Rifka]], [[high jump]]\n* [[Pilar Rold\u00e1n]], [[fencing]]\n* [[Iridia Salazar]], taekwondo\n* [[Oscar Salazar (taekwondo)|Oscar Salazar]], taekwondo\n* [[Mario Santillan]], Paralympian, marathon\n* [[Juan Ren\u00e9 Serrano]], [[archery]]\n* [[Rub\u00e9n Uriza]], equestrian\n* [[Alberto Vald\u00e9s]], equestrian\n* [[Jeny Velazco]], Paralympian, track and field\n* [[Hubertus of Hohenlohe-Langenburg|Hubertus von Hohenlohe]], [[Alpine skiing|alpine skier]]\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Youshimatz|Jos\u00e9 Manuel Youshimatz]], track cycling\n* [[Vanessa Zambotti]], [[judo]]\n* [[Luis Alberto Zepeda F\u00e9lix]], Paralympian, track and field\n\n=== Wrestling ===\n* [[Alfonso Dant\u00e9s|Alfonso Dant\u00e9s, ''El Tanque'']]\n* [[Apolo Dant\u00e9s]]\n* [[Am\u00e9rico Rocca]]\n* [[Atlantis (wrestler)|Atlantis]]\n* [[Black Shadow (wrestler)|Black Shadow]]\n* [[Blue Demon]]\n* [[Blue Panther]]\n* [[Brazo de Plata]] / Super Porky\n* [[Cavernario Galindo]]\n* [[Cien Caras]]\n* [[Charly Manson]]\n* [[Alberto Del Rio]]/ ''Dos Caras, Jr.''\n* [[Dos Caras]]\n* [[Dr. Wagner, Jr.]]\n* [[El Brazo]]\n* [[Canek (wrestler)|El Canek]]\n* [[El Dandy]]\n* [[El Hijo del Santo]]\n* [[El Santo]]\n* [[Emilio Charles, Jr.]]\n* [[Enrique Llanes]]\n* [[Faby Apache]]\n* [[Heavy Metal (wrestler)|Heavy Metal]]\n* [[H\u00e9ctor Garza]]\n* [[Jerry Estrada]]\n* [[La Parka]]\n* [[Lady Apache]]\n* [[Latin Lover (wrestler)|Latin Lover]]\n* [[Lizmark]]\n* [[Lizmark, Jr.]]\n* [[Mari Apache]]\n* [[M\u00e1scara A\u00f1o 2000]]\n* [[M\u00e1scara Sagrada]]\n* [[Mascarita Sagrada]]\n* [[Mil M\u00e1scaras]]\n* [[Miss Janeth]]\n* [[M\u00edstico|M\u00edstico / Sin Cara]]\n* [[Negro Casas]]\n* [[Octag\u00f3n]]\n* [[Octag\u00f3ncito (AAA)|Octagoncito]]\n* [[Perro Aguayo]]\n* [[Perro Aguayo, Jr.]]\n* [[Pierroth, Jr.]]\n* [[Pirata Morgan]]\n* [[Rayo de Jalisco, Jr.]]\n* [[Rayo de Jalisco, Sr.]]\n* [[Ringo Mendoza]]\n* [[Cien Caras|Carmelo Reyes, ''Cien Caras'']]\n* [[Rito Romero]]\n* [[El Sat\u00e1nico|Sat\u00e1nico]]\n* [[Sexy Star]]\n* [[Shocker (wrestler)|Shocker]]\n* [[Scorpio, Jr.]]\n* [[Tarz\u00e1n L\u00f3pez]]\n* [[Villano III]]\n* [[Volador Jr.]]\n* [[Zuleyma]]\n\n=== Other sports ===\n* [[Ra\u00fal Allegre]], [[National Football League|NFL]], [[placekicker]]\n* [[\u00c1lvaro Beltr\u00e1n]], [[racquetball]]\n* [[Rolando Cantu]], NFL, [[offensive guard]]\n* [[Carlos Carsolio]], [[mountaineering]]\n* [[Frank Corral]], NFL, placekicker\n* [[Victor Espinoza]], [[horse racing]]\n* [[Tom Fears]], NFL, [[wide receiver]]\n* [[Martin Garcia (jockey)|Martin Garc\u00eda]], horse racing\n* [[Carlos Gracida]], [[polo]]\n* [[Memo Gracida]], polo\n* [[Efren Herrera|Efr\u00e9n Herrera]], NFL, placekicker\n* [[Leonardo Lavalle]], [[tennis]]\n* [[Victor Leyva]], NFL, offensive guard\n* [[Paola Longoria]], racquetball\n* [[Jorge Lozano]], tennis\n* [[Marco Martos (American football)|Marco Martos]], [[NFL Europe]], wide receiver, head coach\n* [[Lorena Ochoa]], [[golf]]\n* [[Rafael Osuna]], tennis\n* [[Antonio Palafox]], tennis\n* [[Ramiro Pruneda]], NFL, [[offensive tackle]]\n* [[Ra\u00fal Ram\u00edrez]], tennis\n* [[Yola Ram\u00edrez]], tennis\n* [[Ron Rivera]], NFL, player / coach\n* [[Samantha Salas]] racquetball\n* [[Rafael Septi\u00e9n]], NFL, placekicker\n* [[Marcel Sisniega Campbell]], [[chess]]\n* [[Esteban Toledo]], golf\n* [[Carlos Torre Repetto]], chess\n* [[Luis Zendejas]], NFL, placekicker\n* [[Max Zendejas]], NFL, placekicker\n* [[Tony Zendejas]], NFL, placekicker\n\n== See also ==\n{{portal|Biography|Lists|Mexico}}\n*[[List of Mexican Americans]]\n*[[List of Mexican British people]]\n\n{{clear}}\n\n== References ==\n{{reflist}}\n\n[[Category:Lists of Mexican people|*]]\n", "text_old": "{{short description|Wikimedia list article}}\nThis article contains a list of well-known Mexicans in science, publication, arts, politics and sports.\n{| border=1 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 align=right width=275px\n|+<span style=\"font-size:140%;\">'''Estados Unidos Mexicanos'''</span>\n|-\n| style=background:#ffffff; align=center colspan=2 |\n{| border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0\n|-\n| align=\"center\" width=\"160\" | [[Image:Flag of Mexico.svg|140px|right|alt=Flag with green stripe on the left, a red stripe on the right, and in between a white stripe with Mexico's coat-of-arms image|Flag of Mexico]] || align=center width=140px | [[Image:Coat of arms of Mexico.svg|120px|right|Mexican coat of arms|alt=Coat of arms image with large brown bird in center, holding a snake in its beak, and standing on a cactus with leaves and ribbons below|Mexican Coat of Arms]]\n|-\n| align=\"center\" width=\"160\" | <small>([[Flag of Mexico]])</small> || align=center width=140px | <small>([[Mexican coat of arms|Coat of Arms]])</small>\n|}\n|-\n|}\n\n{{Lists of Mexicans}}\n\n== Arts ==\n{{see also|List of Mexican architects|List of Mexican artists}}\n[[File:Amado Nervo.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Amado Nervo]]\n[[File:Frida Kahlo, by Guillermo Kahlo.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Frida Kahlo]]\n[[File:Jose Clemente.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Jos\u00e9 Clemente Orozco]]\n[[File:Diego Rivera with a xoloitzcuintle dog in the Blue House, Coyoacan - Google Art Project.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Diego Rivera]]\n[[File:David Alfaro Siqueiros (El Coronelazo).jpg|thumb|right|upright|David Alfaro Siqueiros]]\n[[File:Rufino Tamayo.jpg|thumb|right|upright|Rufino Tamayo]]\n* [[Manuel \u00c1lvarez Bravo]], photographer; recipient, 1984 [[Hasselblad Award]]\n* [[Pita Amor]], poet\n* [[Alberto Arai]], architect, theorist and writer\n* [[Luis Barrag\u00e1n]], architect\n* [[Federico Cant\u00fa Garza|Federico Cant\u00fa]], painter\n* [[Leonora Carrington]], painter\n* [[Max Cetto]], architec