]], [[Formula One]]\n* [[Israel Jaitovich]], NASCAR, [[road racing|road racer]]\n* [[Michel Jourdain, Jr.]], CART, NASCAR and rallying\n* [[Sergio P\u00e9rez|Sergio ''Checo'' P\u00e9rez]], Formula One\n* [[Jo Ram\u00edrez]], team coordinator Formula One\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Luis Ram\u00edrez (NASCAR)|Jos\u00e9 Luis Ram\u00edrez]], NASCAR\n* [[H\u00e9ctor Rebaque|H\u00e9ctor Alonso Rebaque]], Formula One, CART\n* [[Pedro Rodr\u00edguez (racing driver)|Pedro Rodr\u00edguez]], Formula One\n* [[Ricardo Rodr\u00edguez (Formula One)|Ricardo Rodr\u00edguez]], Formula One\n* [[Memo Rojas|Memo Rojas, Jr.]], [[Rolex Sports Car Series]]\n* [[Mois\u00e9s Solana]], Formula One\n* [[Daniel Su\u00e1rez]], NASCAR\n* [[Ricardo Trivi\u00f1o]], rallying\n\n=== Olympic and Paralympian athletes ===\n* [[Ra\u00fal Alcal\u00e1]], [[bicycle road racing]]\n* [[Daniel Bautista]], [[racewalking]]\n* [[Perla Bustamante]], [[Paralympian]], [[track and field]]\n* [[Ernesto Canto]], racewalking\n* [[Joaqu\u00edn Capilla]], [[diving (sport)|diving]]\n* [[Alejandro C\u00e1rdenas]], track and field\n* [[Everardo Crist\u00f3bal|Everardo Crist\u00f3bal Quirino]], [[canoe racing]]\n* [[Nancy Contreras]], [[track cycling]]\n* [[Paola Espinosa]], diving\n* [[Mar\u00eda del Rosario Espinoza]], [[taekwondo]]\n* [[V\u00edctor Estrada]], taekwondo\n* [[Adriana Fern\u00e1ndez]], [[marathon runner]]\n* [[\u00c1lvaro Gaxiola]], diving\n* [[Carlos Gir\u00f3n]], diving\n* [[Rodolfo G\u00f3mez]], marathon runner\n* [[Ra\u00fal Gonz\u00e1lez (racewalker)|Ra\u00fal Gonz\u00e1lez]], racewalking\n* [[Belem Guerrero]], track cycling\n* [[Ana Gabriela Guevara]], track and field\n* [[Salvador Hernandez]], Paralympian, track and field\n* [[Soraya Jim\u00e9nez Mendivil|Soraya Jim\u00e9nez]], [[weightlifter]]\n* [[Brenda Maga\u00f1a]], [[gymnast]]\n* [[Sa\u00fal Mendoza]], Paralympian, [[wheelchair racer]]\n* [[Humberto Mariles]], [[equestrianism|equestrian]]\n* [[Carlos Mercenario]], racewalking\n* [[Felipe Mu\u00f1oz|Felipe ''Tibio'' Mu\u00f1oz]], swimming\n* [[Rommel Pacheco]], diving\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Pedraza (racewalker)|Jos\u00e9 ''Sargento'' Pedraza]], racewalker\n* [[Guillermo P\u00e9rez (taekwondo)|Guillermo P\u00e9rez]] Sandoval, taekwondo\n* [[Fernando Platas]], diving\n* [[Maria Teresa Ram\u00edrez]], swimming\n* [[Romary Rifka]], [[high jump]]\n* [[Pilar Rold\u00e1n]], [[fencing]]\n* [[Iridia Salazar]], taekwondo\n* [[Oscar Salazar (taekwondo)|Oscar Salazar]], taekwondo\n* [[Mario Santillan]], Paralympian, marathon\n* [[Juan Ren\u00e9 Serrano]], [[archery]]\n* [[Rub\u00e9n Uriza]], equestrian\n* [[Alberto Vald\u00e9s]], equestrian\n* [[Jeny Velazco]], Paralympian, track and field\n* [[Hubertus of Hohenlohe-Langenburg|Hubertus von Hohenlohe]], [[Alpine skiing|alpine skier]]\n* [[Jos\u00e9 Youshimatz|Jos\u00e9 Manuel Youshimatz]], track cycling\n* [[Vanessa Zambotti]], [[judo]]\n* [[Luis Alberto Zepeda F\u00e9lix]], Paralympian, track and field\n\n=== Wrestling ===\n* [[Alfonso Dant\u00e9s|Alfonso Dant\u00e9s, ''El Tanque'']]\n* [[Apolo Dant\u00e9s]]\n* [[Am\u00e9rico Rocca]]\n* [[Atlantis (wrestler)|Atlantis]]\n* [[Black Shadow (wrestler)|Black Shadow]]\n* [[Blue Demon]]\n* [[Blue Panther]]\n* [[Brazo de Plata]] / Super Porky\n* [[Cavernario Galindo]]\n* [[Cien Caras]]\n* [[Charly Manson]]\n* [[Alberto Del Rio]]/ ''Dos Caras, Jr.''\n* [[Dos Caras]]\n* [[Dr. Wagner, Jr.]]\n* [[El Brazo]]\n* [[Canek (wrestler)|El Canek]]\n* [[El Dandy]]\n* [[El Hijo del Santo]]\n* [[El Santo]]\n* [[Emilio Charles, Jr.]]\n* [[Enrique Llanes]]\n* [[Faby Apache]]\n* [[Heavy Metal (wrestler)|Heavy Metal]]\n* [[H\u00e9ctor Garza]]\n* [[Jerry Estrada]]\n* [[La Parka]]\n* [[Lady Apache]]\n* [[Latin Lover (wrestler)|Latin Lover]]\n* [[Lizmark]]\n* [[Lizmark, Jr.]]\n* [[Mari Apache]]\n* [[M\u00e1scara A\u00f1o 2000]]\n* [[M\u00e1scara Sagrada]]\n* [[Mascarita Sagrada]]\n* [[Mil M\u00e1scaras]]\n* [[Miss Janeth]]\n* [[M\u00edstico|M\u00edstico / Sin Cara]]\n* [[Negro Casas]]\n* [[Octag\u00f3n]]\n* [[Octag\u00f