{"title_page": "Bing Crosby filmography", "text_new": "[[File:Bing Crosby poster.JPG|thumb|right|220px|Poster for ''Sing, Bing, Sing'' (1933)]]\nThis is a filmography for the American singer and actor [[Bing Crosby]].<ref name=\"imdb\">{{cite web|title=Bing Crosby |publisher=Internet Movie Database |url=https://www.imdb.com/name/nm0001078/ |accessdate=August 3, 2012}}</ref><ref name=\"allmusic\">{{cite web|title=Bing Crosby |publisher=Allmovie |url=http://www.allmovie.com/artist/bing-crosby-p15874 |accessdate=August 3, 2012}}</ref><ref name=\"tcm\">{{cite web|title=Bing Crosby |publisher=Turner Classic Movies |url=http://www.tcm.com/tcmdb/person/41424%7C22133/Bing-Crosby/filmography-with-synopsis.html |accessdate=August 3, 2012}}</ref><ref name=\"nytimes\">{{cite news|title=Bing Crosby Filmography |newspaper=The New York Times |url=https://movies.nytimes.com/person/15874/Bing-Crosby/filmography |accessdate=August 3, 2012}}</ref>\n\n==Films==\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! style=\"width:50px;\"|Year\n! style=\"width:200px;\"|Title\n! style=\"width:200px;\"|Role\n! class=\"unsortable\" | Notes\n|-\n| 1930\n| ''[[King of Jazz]]''\n| Vocalist\n| Member of \"[[The Rhythm Boys]]\"\n|-\n| 1930\n| ''[[Reaching for the Moon (1930 film)|Reaching for the Moon]]''\n| Bing\n| Short guest appearance to sing one song\n|-\n| 1931\n| ''[[Confessions of a Co-Ed]]''\n| Vocalist\n| Member of The Rhythm Boys\n|-\n| 1931\n| ''[[I Surrender Dear (1931 film)|I Surrender Dear]]''\n| Himself\n| Two-reeler; plays himself; directed by [[Mack Sennett]]\n|-\n| 1931\n| ''[[One More Chance (1931 film)|One More Chance]]''\n| Bing Bangs\n| Two-reeler; directed by Mack Sennett\n|-\n| 1932\n| ''[[Dream House (1931 film)|Dream House]]''\n| Bing Fawcett\n| Two-reeler; produced by Mack Sennett\n|-\n| 1932\n| ''[[Billboard Girl]]''\n| Himself\n| Two-reeler; produced by Mack Sennett\n|-\n| 1932\n| ''[[The Big Broadcast]]''\n| Himself\n| His first starring role in a full-length film.\n|-\n| 1933\