0131307|publisher=Tuckwell Press, East Linton|year=1998|isbn=978-1862320314}}\n{{refend}}\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons category|Robert the Bruce}}\n* [http://www.brucetrust.co.uk/trust.html The Robert the Bruce Commemoration Trust]\n* [http://skyelander.orgfree.com/menu4.html Account of Robert Bruce & Battle of Bannockburn]\n* [https://facebook.com/RobertTheBruceDinner/ Annual Commemorative Robert the Bruce Dinner]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20100721024820/http://www.robertthebruceheritagecentre.co.uk/ Robert the Bruce Heritage Centre]\n* {{NPG name|name=Robert I ('The Bruce')}}\n\n{{s-start}}\n{{s-hou | [[House of Bruce]] ||11 July 1274||7 June 1329}}\n{{s-bef|before=[[Marjorie of Carrick, 3rd Countess of Carrick|Marjorie]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Earl of Carrick]]|years=1292\u20131314}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Edward Bruce|Edward]]}}\n|-\n{{s-bef|before=[[Robert de Brus, jure uxoris Earl of Carrick|Robert VI de Brus]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[Lord of Annandale]]|years=1304\u20131312}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[Thomas Randolph, 1st Earl of Moray|Thomas Randolph]]}}\n{{s-reg | }}\n|-\n{{s-vac|last=[[John of Scotland|John]]}}\n{{s-ttl|title=[[King of Scotland]]|years=1306\u20131329}}\n{{s-aft|after=[[David II of Scotland|David II]]}}\n{{s-end}}\n\n{{Pictish and Scottish Monarchs}}\n{{Earls of Carrick}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Robert the Bruce}}\n[[Category:1274 births]]\n[[Category:1329 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from South Ayrshire]]\n[[Category:House of Bruce]]\n[[Category:Guardians of Scotland]]\n[[Category:Norman warriors]]\n[[Category:Scoto-Normans]]\n[[Category:Earls or mormaers of Carrick]]\n[[Category:13th-century mormaers]]\n[[Category:14th-century Scottish earls]]\n[[Category:Scottish folklore]]\n[[Category:Scottish people of the Wars of Scottish Independence]]\n[[Category:Scottish knights]]\n[[Category:Scottish generals]]\n[[Category:Scottish rebels]]\n[[Category:Burials at Dunfermline Abbey]]\n[[Category:People temporarily excommunicated by the Catholic 