, 112, 186, 240, 231, 365, 299, 319, 292, 418, 499, 509, 471\n|y1Title=New deaths per day\n|yGrid= |xGrid=\n}}\n\n{{Graph:Chart\n|width=550\n|colors=#0000FF\n|showValues=offset:2\n|xAxisTitle=Date\n|xAxisAngle=-40\n|type=rect\n|x= 26 Feb, 27 Feb, 28 Feb, 29 Feb, 1 Mar, 2 Mar, 3 Mar, 4 Mar, 5 Mar, 6 Mar, 7 Mar, 8 Mar, 9 Mar, 10 Mar, 11 Mar, 12 Mar, 13 Mar, 14 Mar, 15 Mar, 16 Mar, 17 Mar, 18 Mar, 19 Mar, 20 Mar, 21 Mar, 22 Mar, 23 Mar, 24 Mar, 25 Mar, 26 Mar, 27 Mar, 28 Mar, 29 Mar, 30 Mar, 31 Mar, 1 Apr, 2 Apr\n|yAxisTitle=Growth factor\n|legend=\n|y1=0.38, 4.00, 0.95, 2.26, 0.70, 2.03, 0.34, 3.48, 1.89, 1.38, 1.93, 0.48, 1.62, 1.30, 1.34, 1.20, 1.32, 1.07, 1.10, 1.31, 0.91, 1.28, 1.33, 0.87, 1.14, 1.21, 1.42, 0.77, 1.20, 1.34, 0.97, 1.21, 0.56, 1.68, 1.73, 0.64, 0.44\n|y1Title=Growth factor\n|yGrid= |xGrid=\n}}\n\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n|+\n'''Situation on 27 March 2020'''<ref name=\"linternaute2489651\">{{cite web|url=https://www.linternaute.com/actualite/guide-vie-quotidienne/2489651-covid-19-en-france-nombre-de-cas-de-coronavirus-reanimations-morts-tous-les-chiffres-du-28-mars-2020/|title=Covid-19 en France : nombre de cas de coronavirus, r\u00e9animations, morts... Tous les chiffres du 28 mars 2020|last=Deshayes|first=Benoit|last2=Linternaute.com|first2=Mis \u00e0 jour le 28/03/20 19:40|website=linternaute.com|language=fr|access-date=28 March 2020}}</ref>\n!Region\n!D\u00e9partement\n!Number of cases\n!Hospitalised\n![[Intensive Care Unit|ICU]]<!-- Resuscitation -->\n!Recovered\n!Dead\n|-\n| rowspan=\"12\" |Auvergne \u2013 Rh\u00f4ne Alpes\n|Ain\n| rowspan=\"12\" |{{#invoke:String|match|{{#invoke:wd|properties|normal+|Q87143769|P1603|sep=X}}|[^X]*$}}\n|49\n|9\n|17\n|2\n|-\n|Allier\n|18\n|2\n|27\n|4\n|-\n|Ard\u00e8che\n|54\n|9\n|45\n|9\n|-\n|Cantal\n|7\n|4\n|2\n|0\n|-\n|Dr\u00f4me\n|129\n|35\n|39\n|21\n|-\n|Is\u00e8re\n|114\n|29\n|52\n|4\n|-\n|Loire\n|262\n|51\n|44\n|20\n|-\n|Haute-Loire\n|14\n|6\n|12\n|1\n|-\n|Puy-de-D\u00f4me\n|27\n|5\n|14\n|0\n|-\n|Rh\u00f4ne